				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">This article is about <a href="/wiki/Video_game" title="Video game">video game</a> design, and does not deal with the design of other forms of <a href="/wiki/Game" title="Game">game</a>, such as <a href="/wiki/Board_game" title="Board game">board games</a> and <a href="/wiki/Card_game" title="Card game">card games</a>.</div>
