<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/dp/B0052QA5WU">The Art of Computer Game Design</a> by <a href="/wiki/Chris_Crawford_(game_designer)" title="Chris Crawford (game designer)">Chris Crawford</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.dmoz.org/Games/Video_Games/Game_Design/">Game design</a> at the <a href="/wiki/Open_Directory_Project" title="Open Directory Project">Open Directory Project</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.runawaystudios.com/articles/chris_taylor_gdd.asp">Example Game Design Document</a> by Chris Taylor</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.gamespot.com/features/so-you-wanna-be-a-game-designer-6129276/">"So You Wanna Be a Game Designer"</a> at <i><a href="/wiki/GameSpot" title="GameSpot">GameSpot</a></i></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://web.archive.org/web/20080107182604/http://www.eurocom.co.uk/content/view/102/81/">The Designer</a> at <a href="/wiki/Eurocom" title="Eurocom">Eurocom</a></li>
</ul>
