<ul>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://groups.google.com/groups/dir?hl=en&amp;lr=&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;q=comp.games.development.design">comp.games.development.design</a> via <a href="/wiki/Google_Groups" title="Google Groups">Google Groups</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://groups.google.com/groups/dir?hl=en&amp;lr=&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;q=rec.games.design">rec.games.design</a> via <a href="/wiki/Google_Groups" title="Google Groups">Google Groups</a></li>
